  "text": "Cell migration was assessed by the ability of cells to move into an acellular area in a two-dimensional scratch assay [CITATION_1] . Fibroblasts (2.5 x 10 5 cells/well) were treated and a scratch was made in the center of the well with a 100 μl pipette tip. The denuded area was measured soon after scratching and at 1, 2 and 3 days later. The results were expressed as the percentage of the initial denuded area.",
